Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web

Class BaseStatGenerator<T extends Cloudlet>

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web.BaseStatGenerator<T>
Type Parameters:
T - - the actual type of the generated CloudLets.
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGenerator<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
StatGenerator
public abstract class BaseStatGenerator<T extends Cloudlet> extends Object implements IGenerator<T>
A base class containing the main functionality of a statistical generator of CloutLets. This class generates CloudLets based on the provided statistical distributions for their properties. Random generators are provided in a map, whose keys usually are the constants of the class, as documented below.
Author:
nikolay.grozev

      Creates a new generator with the specified statistical distributions.

      startTime - - the start time of the generation. If positive, no web cloudlets with ideal start time before this will be generated.
